### 2.3 API Layer

#### [NEW] `src/lib/api.ts`
- Axios instance with `baseURL: http://localhost:3000/api`
- Request interceptor: attach JWT token from Zustand store
- Response interceptor: handle 401 в†’ redirect to login, handle errors globally

#### [NEW] `src/services/*.service.ts` (7 files)
Each service maps 1:1 to the backend route groups. Example:

```typescript
// upi.service.ts
export const upiService = {
  payP2P: (data: PayP2PRequest) => api.post('/upi/pay', data),
  payMerchant: (data: PayMerchantRequest) => api.post('/upi/pay/merchant', data),
  createCollect: (data: CollectRequest) => api.post('/upi/collect', data),
  respondToCollect: (id: string, data: CollectResponse) => api.post(`/upi/collect/${id}/respond`, data),
  getPendingCollects: () => api.get('/upi/collect/pending'),
  getTransactionHistory: (params: TransactionQuery) => api.get('/upi/transactions', { params }),
  refundTransaction: (data: RefundRequest) => api.post('/upi/refund', data),
};
```

