| `useAuthStore` | `user`, `token`, `isAuthenticated` | `login()`, `register()`, `logout()`, `hydrate()` |
| `useAccountStore` | `accounts`, `balance`, `activeAccountId` | `fetchAccounts()`, `fetchBalance()`, `createAccount()` |
| `useNotificationStore` | `notifications`, `unreadCount` | `fetch()`, `markRead()` |

### 2.5 Page Implementations

#### Login & Register (`/login`, `/register`)
- Email + password form with Zod validation
- JWT token stored in Zustand (persisted to localStorage)
- Redirect to `/dashboard` on success
- Error toast on failure

#### Dashboard (`/dashboard`)
- **BalanceCard**: Large balance display with account selector
- **QuickActions**: Send Money, Request Money, Scan QR (4-grid layout)
- **RecentTransactions**: Last 5 transactions with "View All" link
- Skeleton loading states
- Pull-to-refresh pattern

#### Send Money (`/send`)
- Step 1: Enter receiver VPA в†’ resolve to display name (`GET /api/upi-id/resolve/:vpa`)
- Step 2: Enter amount with numeric display
- Step 3: Enter UPI PIN в†’ confirm
- Step 4: Success / failure animation
- Idempotency key generated client-side (`crypto.randomUUID()`)

#### Request Money (`/request`)
- Enter payer VPA + amount + optional note
- Calls `POST /api/upi/collect`
- Pending collect requests list (`GET /api/upi/collect/pending`)
- Approve/decline flow for incoming requests

#### Transaction History (`/transactions`)
- Paginated list from `GET /api/upi/transactions`
- Filter tabs: All | Sent | Received | Failed
- Date grouping (Today, Yesterday, This Week, etc.)
- Status badges with colors (green=COMPLETED, red=FAILED, yellow=PENDING)

#### Profile (`/profile`)
- User info card (name, email)
- VPA management (list, create, set default, deactivate)
- Linked bank accounts (list, link, verify, set primary)
- Dark/Light mode toggle
- Logout button

